collectionMetadata.name: Number of Graduates in Healthcare Specialisations by Course
collectionMetadata.description:
List of schools:

* Medical Graduates: NUS Yong Loo Lin School of Medicine and Duke-NUS Graduate Medical School (from 2011 onwards) graduates.
* Nursing Graduates: NUS (from 2009 onwards), NYP, NP and ITE nursing graduates, including graduates from WDA's Professional Conversion Programmes (from 2005 onwards). 
* Allied Health Professionals Graduates: NYP Physiotherapy, Occupational Therapy, Diagnostic Radiography and Radiation Therapy graduates, including graduates from WDA's Professional Conversion Programmes (from 2011 onwards), NUS Speech and Language Pathology (Biennial intake (2-year programme) from 2007 onwards). 
* Dentists Graduated: NUS Faculty of Dentistry graduates.
* Oral Health Therapists Graduated: Nanyang Polytechnic Dental Hygiene and Therapy graduates.
* Pharmacists Graduated: NUS Department of Pharmacy graduates.

The first batch of Oral Health Therapists graduated in 2008.
